    <h1>OTTO Market</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>OTTO market is OTTO’s marketplace. You are shown as the seller of your products. However, communication with customers is managed by OTTO.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="100">1. Overview of automatic data exchange</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>After setting up OTTO Market in plentymarkets, the automatic processes described in <a href="#data-exchange-market">Table 1</a> are available:</p>
</div>
<table id="data-exchange-market" class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch">
<caption class="title">Table 1. Frequency of data exchange</caption>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 40%;">
<col style="width: 60%;">
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Data</th>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Interval</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Item export</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>once per night</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Price synchronisation</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>once per night at the time of item export</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Stock synchronisation</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
